`createdAt` and `updatedAt` are fields which rarely miss from collections of modern applications.

I suggest implementing this through a toggle parameter which when enabled, a trait would be injected in the model to implement those additional fields, and also bind to the `lifecycle` events to ensure the values are created/updated automatically.

